data.text:
Turtledove, Harry.

New York: Ballantine Books, [1996]. Octavo, cloth-backed boards. First edition. Last book of a four-volume alternate history series set during World War II, preceded by WORLDWAR: IN THE BALANCE, WORLDWAR: TILTING THE BALANCE, and WORLDWAR: UPSETTING THE BALANCE. Review slip and publisher's publicity sheet laid in. A fine copy in fine dust jacket. (#169530) (30152). Item #30152
